n></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-language=
:ZH-CN">I am replying to acknowledge receipt of the letter, and to further =
acknowledge that Abigail will be copied into all correspondence moving forw=
ard.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-language=
:ZH-CN">I have requested that the appointed specialists provide dates and t=
imes when they can be available.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-language=
:ZH-CN">I am proposing that the following persons complete site visit, asse=
ssing &amp; testing, as a necessary pre-requisite to providing relevant rep=
orts for all stakeholders to review:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-language=
:ZH-CN"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
